OL,3,CMan admits throwing traffic cone at
OL,4,Cpolice during Southampton protests
OL,6,FA man has admitted throwing a traffic
OL,7,Fcone at police during protests in
OL,8,FSouthampton sparked by the murder of
OL,9,Funiversity student Henry Nowak.
OL,11,FConnor Bishop, 24, pleaded guilty to
OL,12,Fviolent disorder at Southampton
OL,13,FMagistrates' Court on Friday afternoon.
OL,15,FProsecutor Kevin Lucie said CCTV
OL,16,Ffootage showed Bishop "picking up and
OL,17,Fthrowing a traffic cone" at police
OL,18,Fduring a protest following the
OL,19,Fsentencing of Vickrum Digwa for the
OL,20,Fmurder of 18-year-old Mr Nowak in
OL,21,FDecember.
OL,26,@xD@WOUyD@XO]
