CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780826741
OL,3,CMan admits throwing traffic cone at
OL,4,Cpolice during Southampton protests
OL,6,FViolent protests erupted after Digwa
OL,7,Fclaimed he had been the victim of a
OL,8,Fracial attack, while Mr Nowak was
OL,9,Fhandcuffed by police who ignored his
OL,10,Fpleas that he could not breathe as he
OL,11,Flay dying.
OL,13,FMr Lucie said Bishop attended a
OL,14,Fprotest at Southampton Central Police
OL,15,FStation on Tuesday evening with a
OL,16,Flarge group of people and was among
OL,17,Fthose who followed retreating police
OL,18,Fofficers.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
