FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780826741
OL,3,CMan admits throwing traffic cone at
OL,4,Cpolice during Southampton protests
OL,6,FThe prosecutor added that Bishop, of
OL,7,FOxford Street, Southampton, became
OL,8,Fpart of the disorder with several of
OL,9,Fthe group throwing wheelie bins at
OL,10,Fpolice.
OL,12,FThe court heard that Bishop "refused
OL,13,Fto come up" from the cells for his
OL,14,Fcourt hearing and a guilty plea was
OL,15,Fentered by his lawyer Will Day.
OL,17,FDistrict Judge Anthony Callaway
OL,18,Fremanded Bishop in custody and he will
OL,19,Fbe sentenced at Southampton Crown
OL,20,FCourt on Monday.
OL,26,@tD@]OUuD@KO]
