PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780826741
OL,3,CMan admits throwing traffic cone at
OL,4,Cpolice during Southampton protests
OL,6,FReece Robinson, 21, of Soberton Road,
OL,7,FHavant, and Noah Etherington, 18, of
OL,8,FRowbury Road, Havant, both pleaded
OL,9,Fguilty at Portsmouth Magistrates'
OL,10,FCourt on Friday to violent disorder, a
OL,11,Fcourts official said.
OL,13,FThe two were remanded into custody and
OL,14,Fwill be sentenced on Monday at
OL,15,FSouthampton Crown Court.
OL,17,FDaniel Frost, 44, of Southampton,
OL,18,Fpleaded guilty on Thursday to violent
OL,19,Fdisorder and possessing a dog lead
OL,20,Fwith a metal carabiner as an offensive
OL,21,Fweapon following the protests.
